			var src ="//in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/website/banner/large/super-30-et00064569-03-11-2017-12-22-53.jpg", imgSrc = "//in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/website/poster/large/super-30-et00064569-03-11-2017-12-22-53.jpg";			function fnChangeUrl(pathName) {
				try {
					var myURL = window.location.pathname.substr(0, window.location.pathname.indexOf("movies"));
					window.location = myURL+"movies/"+pathName;

					BMS.Misc.fnErr({ fnName : "fnChangeUrl", err : e });

                        						<div id="mv-summary" class="tab-content" style="display: none;">
                                                    <div class="__heading">SYNOPSIS</div>
                            <div class="synopsis">
                               <blockquote cite="http://in.bookmyshow.com/movies/super-30/ET00064569">
									Anand Kumar, a Mathematics genius from a modest family in Bihar who is made to believe that only a King's son can become a king is on a mission to prove that even the poor man can create some of the world's most genius minds. He starts a training program named 'Super 30' to help 30 IIT aspirants crack the entrance test and make them highly successful professionals.  								</blockquote>
                            </div>

	<span class="__verified"><span class="__verified-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" enable-background="new 0 0 100 100" xml:space="preserve"><use xlink:href="/icons/common-icons.svg#icon-vtick"></use></svg></span><span class="__verified-text">Verified Review</span></span>|<span class="__timestamp">12/7/19</span>									  </span></div><div class="__reviewer-text">Everyone who loved Hrithik in Jodha Akbar, Kites and Guzaarish will very much love Hrithik's screen presence and brilliant performance through out the movie. Personally as a fan, it was really tough to imagine Hrithik performing this character, but sometime during the movie you'll forget the handsome, stylish Hrithik whom you loved and see an extraordinary actor shining in front of you. That's how he wins over you.
For record, I believe Super 30 will remain as his career best as far his acting goes. A big congrats  to Hrithik Roshan 👏👏👏

And with acting, it's not just Hrithik who shines, but everyone. Even the little emotions were handled so well, that it brought the best of everyone. Well done, #VikasBahl. 👏👏👏

#MrinalThakur appears real cute ♥️ in screen but doesn't have much role to play, cause this movie is all about Anand Kumar and his Super 30. 

The only issue which I see with this movie would be the commercialisation which pops every now and then. But if brilliant acting, cinematography, heart throbbing BGMs and sound design amuses you, then commercialism is something which you can ignore. With that said, the movie has its own tearjerking moments, so yeah, carry your hankie, if you are emotional 😜

Watch Super 30 in a really good theatre.  You'll never regret the experience.😍</div></div></div><div class="mv-synopsis-review"><div class="__reviewer-face"><div class="wow __reviewer-image-area" style="visibility: visible;"><img class="__timestamp">14/7/19</span>									  </span></div><div class="__reviewer-text">The movie is pictured on a real story of Anand Kumar, a Bihari, lower middle class belonging boy whose passion for mathematics reaches him heights inspite of not being able to vouch his offer of studying at Cambridge university. He is flowen out with chances to flourish economically but rather chooses to educate the unprivileged children aspiring to be admitted in IIT since he himself has walked the same path. His strong mentally driven desire to authorise the deserving sets out challenges for him till the end. The trailers haven’t caught up well maybe specially with the comments that seem to have turned off a lot of audiences talking about Hrithik’s Bihari lingo and tan face. But once you start watching the movie, every bit of it starts soaking you into the character and makes you feel alive. First half is extremely entertaining, second half gets a bit boring and might seem slightly unrealistic however the central idea of the movie has been put out really well. The end will make you feel inspired and positive. A must watch for sure.</div></div></div><div class="mv-synopsis-review"><div class="__reviewer-face"><div class="wow __reviewer-image-area" style="visibility: visible;"><img 10,6.00250244 C10,9.50421143 6.5,12.49823 1.99816895,16.496582 C1.65066553,16.8052211 0.984609214,17.4230271 0,18.35 L0,2 Z"></path></g></svg></span></span><span class="__reviewer-foot"> 									  	<span class="__verified"><span class="__verified-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" enable-background="new 0 0 100 100" xml:space="preserve"><use xlink:href="/icons/common-icons.svg#icon-vtick"></use></svg></span><span class="__verified-text">Verified Review</span></span>|<span class="__timestamp">17/7/19</span>									  </span></div><div class="__reviewer-text">एक ठो बात करना था आपसे,
यह जितना भी लोगवा है न, जो लिखता है कि ह्रितिक का बोली बिहार का नहीं न है, उसका आंख का रंग ठीक नहीं न है, उसका एक्टिंगव और किसी फिल्म से मेल खाता है, फ़िल्म का डायरेक्शन थोड़ा कम अच्छा है, फ़िल्म का लम्बाई ससुर ज्यादा है, अउर तो अऊर कहानीबा भी ससुर असली नहीं है, आएसा सब बातों पर और  ऐसा सब लोगों पर मिट्टी डालिये अउर सुपर स्पीडबा लगाइये और जा कर फिलम देख लीजिए, बस। हमारा बात खतम।

रहा उनसब लोगों का बात जो एक महीने से  ससुर लिखा जा रहा है कि फ़िल्म में यह कमी रह गया वो कमी रह गया ,वास्तव में ससुर देखा ही नहीं है उसे । हम तो कहता हूं बड़ा पोलटिक्स है ससुर रिव्यू लिखने में। यहां भी पैसा खाता है पत्रकार लोग , हमारा सुन लीजिए या कंगना का बात।
 जो सही है सो सही है बस।

बात जुनून का है, पूरा फ़िलम ही उही बात पर है, जो जुनून ही न समझे ससुर फ़िलम क्या समझेगा!  बायोपिक फ़ायोपिक का बात अलग रखिये , क्या है कि क्रटिसायज़ करने के लिए अंग्रेज़ी का कौनो वर्ड तो चहिये ही हुआ न ।

आप पिक्चर में बस बैठ जाइए फिर जो कहिये सो सचवा रहा बाकी सब झूठ। रहा कहानी का सच साहेब सब बाहर आजयेगा, क्या है कि जिनकी कहानी है वे अभी जिंदा है , आज नहीं तो कल बोल ही देंगे।

अब कुछ लाइन रिव्यू का भी लिख दें। ससुर बहुत कमाल किये हैं ह्रितिक हर बार की तरह। पर बहुत दिनों बाद वीरो (हमारा वीरेंद्र सक्सेना) ने भी हद कर दिया है ,ससुर रुला ही दिए है कई बार। कृष्णमोहन सक्सेना भाईसाहब से कहता हूं कि हमारा बात वीरो तक पहुंचा दे।
बाकी सब का एक्टिंग भी अच्छा है, संगीत खूब ही अच्छा है ।

एक ठो यह बात भी कि जब पिक्चर बना रहा है कोई तो क्या पिक्चर बनाने का स्वतंत्रता नहीं दीजियेगा उसे  ?

यह साढ़े तीन स्टार देने वालों का ऐसी का तैसी हम तो एक स्टार और देते है  करना है कर लीजिए पर पहले ठंडे दिमाग से सुपर 30 में शामिल तो होइए।

हम तो वैसे भी थोड़े भुक्त भोगी भी रहे कि  आईआईटी के एग्जाम में बैठ ही नही पाए क्योंकि हमारी एप्लिकेशन में से किसी डाक वाले आदमी ने वह ससुर पोस्टल आर्डर ही निकाल लिए और फिर तरिखबा ही निकल गया सो आईआईटी न जा सके। एमएससी मेथमेटिक करते रहे गये। सो सवाल तो हमारा मन में भी ससुर बहुत से रहा पर 
आप इधर उधर का छोड़िए बस !!</div></div></div><div class="mv-synopsis-review"><div class="__reviewer-face"><div class="wow __reviewer-image-area" style="visibility: visible;"><img <script type="text/javascript">
  var clevertap = {event:[], profile:[], account:[], onUserLogin:[], notifications:[]};
  // wizrocket.account.push({"id":"RK6-Z85-W44Z"});
      clevertap.account.push({"id": "RK4-47R-98KZ"});
  
  (function () {
     var wzrk = document.createElement('script');
     wzrk.type = 'text/javascript';
     wzrk.async = true;
     wzrk.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://d2r1yp2w7bby2u.cloudfront.net' : 'http://static.clevertap.com') + '/js/a.js';
     var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
     s.parentNode.insertBefore(wzrk, s);
  })();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  if ( BMS.Storage.get({name:"ld", "key":"MEMBERID", storage: "C"}) != "" ) {
    if (typeof(clevertap) !== "undefined") {
      clevertap.profile.push({
        "Site": {
          "Identity" : BMS.Storage.get({name:"ld", "key":"MEMBERID", storage: "C"}),
          "Email" : BMS.Storage.get({name:"ld", "key":"MEMBEREMAIL", storage: "C"}),
          "Phone" : "+91" + $.trim(BMS.Storage.get({name:"ld", "key":"MOBILE", storage: "C"})),
          "App Language" : $("#dLangWrap [data-val='" + (BMS.Storage.get({ name: "lang", storage: "C" }) || "eng") + "']").attr("data-name")
        }
      });
    }
  }
</script>

  jQuery(document).ready(function() {
    if(pageName != 'buytickets') { //Ali added this to avoid freeze on render for IE
      svg4everybody();
    }

    window.setTimeout(function() {

      //Add condtion for checking if user has selected the region
      if(BMS.Storage.isset({name:'Rgn'})) {
        BMS.Misc.fnPushNotificationsFromClevertap();
      }
    }, 5000); //Execute after 5000 ms

  });

		<script type="text/javascript">
			$(document).ready(function(){
				try {
					/* Temporary Changes for Mobile - BEGIN */
					if (BMS.Misc.fnGQS("app") == "native") {
						$(".like-rating").css("margin-left", "10px");
						$(".synopsis-banner").css("margin-top", "0px");
					}
					/* Temporary Changes for Mobile - END */
						var img = $("<img src='"+src+"'/>");
						img.error(function(e){
							$("#imgBanner").css('background-image','url('+global.strContentUrl+'/webin/movies/default.jpg)');
						});
						window.global.SAEventCodes = eventCodeArray;
						window.SAData.get();
					setTimeout(function(){
								try{
									BMS.Misc.fnPushEventDataToAnalytics(["WR","KM","WN"],"Viewed synopsis",{
										 "ProductID":"ET00064569",
										 "Event Type":"MT",
										 "Event Name":"Super 30",
										 "Genre":"Biography, Drama",
										 "Language":"Hindi",
										 "Event Group":"EG00044778",
										 "Overall rating":"87",
										 "Critics rating":"70",
										 "Cast and Crew":"Hrithik Roshan,Mrunal Thakur,Pankaj Tripathi,Ritvik Sahore,Virendra Saxena,Aditya Srivastava,Kiran Khoje,Nandish Sandhu,Master Ali Haji",
										 "User rating":"90",
										 "Is logged in Viewed Synopsis":BMS.Storage.isset({ name: "ld" })  ? true : false,
										 "Appcode":global.strAppCode,
										 "Release Date": "Jul 12, 2019",
										 "App Language": BMS.Storage.isset({ name: "lang" }) ? BMS.Storage.get({name: 'lang'}) : "eng"
									});

									BMS.Misc.fnPushEventDataToAnalytics(["GA"], "", {}, {
									    "event" : "productdetail",
									    "ecommerce" : {
									  		"currencyCode":"INR",
									  		"detail":{
									  			"actionField":{'list':'Category'},
									  			"products":[{
									  				"name":"Super 30",
									  				"id":"ET00064569",
									  				"brand":"",
									  				"category":"MT",
									  				"variant":"2D",
									  				"dimension13":"Hindi",
									  				"dimension14":"",
									  				"dimension15":BMS.Storage.get({ name: "Rgn", key: "Code" }) +'| PRESSED'
									  			}]
									  		}
									    }
									});
							}catch(e){
							}
							}
						,0);

					var infoBtn = $('.info-icon');
	 				var trailerBtn = $('.trailer-icon');

	 				infoBtn.on('click', infoClickHandler);
					trailerBtn.on('click', trailerClickHandler);

				} catch (e) {
					console.log('Error :: movie-synopsis-v1 -> ', e);
				}
				if ($('#eventTitle').text().length >= 46) {
					$('#eventTitle').css("font-size", 24);
				}
			});

			$(window).load(function() {
				try {
					var widgetType = "";
					if($('.details').find('.mv-coming-soon').length && widgetType == 'movie' && BMS.Storage.isset({ name: "Rgn" })) {
						$('.wts-container').addClass('_blink');
					}
				} catch(e) {
					console.log('Error : synopsis -> ', e);
				}
			});

        	var infoClickHandler = function () {
        		var event_code = $(this).attr("data-id");
        		var event_title = $(this).attr("data-event-title");
        		var position = $(this).attr("data-position");

				BMS.Misc.fnPushEventDataToAnalytics(["GA"], "", {}, {
					'event': 'bms_related_movie_info',
					'movie_id': event_code,
					'position': position,
					'movie_name':event_title
				});
        	};

        	var trailerClickHandler = function () {
	    		var event_code = $(this).attr("data-id");
	    		var event_title = $(this).attr("data-event-title");
